description:
This is a 17 minute workout called '15 min FULL BODY PILATES with WEIGHTS | At Home Pilates Workout Class' from the channel Lilly Sabri.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: This full body pilates workout challenge will help you tone and burn fat with exercises that use weights and bodyweight. It's an intense 15 minute at home pilates workout class that will target your full body from upper body to lower body.
